{% comment %}
  App Embed: Wholesale (site-wide)
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  This is an APP EMBED block (target: "body"), not a section block. It is enabled
  from the theme editor's "App embeds" panel with a single on/off toggle — no
  section placement required, so it can't be put in the wrong spot or forgotten
  on a template. This is the robust, site-wide host for the wholesale UI.

  What it does on every page, for logged-in wholesale customers:
    1. Emits <meta name="wh-customer" content="1"> so wholesale.js knows the
       customer is wholesale instantly — no async status call, no price flash.
    2. Loads wholesale.css + wholesale.js, which power the product-page
       wholesale price block and the account-dropdown Orders link rewrite.
       (Collection/search cards intentionally show no prices — matches the
       theme's cards, which are image + title only.)

  wholesale.js is idempotent (window.__whWholesaleInit guard), so loading it here
  AND from the product-page price block on a PDP is safe.
{% endcomment %}

{% comment %} Shop-wide tag casing registry: writes of 'wholesale' can surface
   as legacy 'Wholesale', so the check must be case-insensitive. {% endcomment %}
{% assign wh_tag_str = customer.tags | join: '|' | downcase | prepend: '|' | append: '|' %}
{% if customer and wh_tag_str contains '|wholesale|' %}
  <meta name="wh-customer" content="1">
  {{ 'wholesale.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}
  <script src="{{ 'wholesale.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>

  {% comment %}
    Header cart button → line sheet icon. The theme cart is irrelevant to
    wholesale ordering (the linesheet is the only ordering surface), so this
    hides the header cart link server-side (no flash) and wholesale.js swaps
    in the linesheet icon at the same spot from this template. The hide CSS
    and the JS insert target the SAME selector, so if the theme's header
    markup ever changes they fail together and the cart button simply returns.
  {% endcomment %}
  {% style %}
    .header__cart .custom-cart-icon { display: none !important; }
  {% endstyle %}
  <template id="wh-header-linesheet-tpl">
    <a
      href="{{ block.settings.linesheet_url | default: '/pages/linesheet' }}"
      class="wh-header-linesheet"
      aria-label="Wholesale order sheet"
    >
      <img src="{{ 'linesheet-icon.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Order sheet" width="77" height="98">
    </a>
  </template>
{% else %}
  <meta name="wh-customer" content="0">
{% endif %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Wholesale (site-wide)",
  "target": "body",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "url",
      "id": "linesheet_url",
      "label": "Linesheet page URL",
      "info": "Where the header icon links to. Defaults to /pages/linesheet."
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
